  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether methamphetamine-dependent individuals will
      use less methamphetamine when treated with naltrexone. The study will also investigate
      whether individuals with the mu opioid receptor gene variant A118G will use less
      methamphetamine than individuals without A118G.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
